DESCRIPTION:Tonight a new season of Big Brother begins. From music\, to fa
 shion\, to social media trends\, there's no denying that nostalgia is ever
 ywhere! And it seems like everyone has a thirst for the past\, and this se
 ason so does Big Brother.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother S28E02
DTSTART:20260713T000000Z
DTEND:20260713T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260722T123409Z
UID:tvmaze-1453-ep-3616872@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:The first Head of Household of BB 28 will be crowned! And the 
 first three nominees of the summer will hit the block. Plus\, is it showma
 nce o'clock already?
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother S28E03
DTSTART:20260716T000000Z
DTEND:20260716T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260722T123409Z
UID:tvmaze-1453-ep-3616873@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:It's the inaugural Veto competition of the season\, with a cou
 ple of BB legends joining the fun. Who will win the Golden Power of Veto? 
 Will it be used to save one of the nominees? Plus\, it took nearly a week\
 , but Angela's first BB breakdown is finally here.
END:VEVENT
